I gotta stop him. though.

753
01:27:24.882 --> 01:27:27.936
I have to. cos I created him.

754
01:27:30.864 --> 01:27:32.718
What do you mean?

755
01:27:33.561 --> 01:27:36.155
I gave him an equation.

756
01:27:38.305 --> 01:27:40.773
I made all of this possible.

757
01:27:48.039 --> 01:27:52.099
Something my father's
been working on. you know?

758
01:27:52.205 --> 01:27:54.652
Secretly. now I realise
why he kept it a secret.

759
01:27:57.037 --> 01:27:59.475
Why this is my responsibility.

760
01:28:02.903 --> 01:28:05.189
