761
01:28:15.382 --> 01:28:17.261
Let's get out of here.

762
01:28:18.105 --> 01:28:22.021
Let's get out of here.
just for a minute. can we?

763
01:28:22.338 --> 01:28:24.283
- No. - Yeah.
- No. - Yes.

764
01:28:24.957 --> 01:28:28.870
If my parents see me leaving I'm dead.

765
01:28:33.796 --> 01:28:36.405
Your parents are not gonna see you leaving.

766
01:28:49.681 --> 01:28:55.731
<i>Peter Parker... Spiderman?
I'm not the one who needs help!</i>

767
01:28:57.137 --> 01:29:00.270
<i>There will be no more
loneliness. no more outcasts!</i>

768
