771
01:29:12.920 --> 01:29:15.354
That. changing like the
snake. I might be free.

772
01:29:15.497 --> 01:29:19.328
To cast off flesh
wherein I dwell confined!

773
01:29:19.363 --> 01:29:23.459
<i>Would you give it all up?
After all you know you can do?</i>

774
01:29:23.578 --> 01:29:26.628
