way of my plan. Peter Parker!</i>

777
01:30:09.426 --> 01:30:11.125
Go. go!

778
01:30:47.174 --> 01:30:49.893
Nowhere to hide. Peter.

779
01:31:06.503 --> 01:31:08.909
All these souls. lost and
alone.

780
01:31:08.999 --> 01:31:11.698
I can save them. I can sure them.

781
01:31:11.775 --> 01:31:14.552
there's no need to stop me. Peter.

782
01:31:24.262 --> 01:31:26.357
You're not thinking straight doc.

783
01:31:29.967 --> 01:31:31.811
Stop this! This isn't you!

784
