Let's talk this out!

785
01:31:38.800 --> 01:31:40.080
Doc!

786
01:31:45.694 --> 01:31:47.102
Oh boy.

787
01:31:51.904 --> 01:31:55.100
Alright. so you don't want to talk?
There you go.

788
01:31:59.150 --> 01:32:01.530
Don't... Make me...

789
