But we need an antidote.
do you know how to run a serum?

797
01:32:51.749 --> 01:32:52.949
<i>Yeah. I do it for
Connors all the time.</i>

798
01:32:53.046 --> 01:32:54.278
Okay great. great great

799
01:32:54.402 --> 01:32:58.115
I need you to go to Oscorp.
<i>I need you to access the cross-species file. </i>

800
01:32:58.227 --> 01:33:01.615
<i>it's a blue serum file 12389.</i>

801
01:33:01.700 --> 01:33:04.077
<i>- OK. got it.</i> On my way.

802
01:33:35.616 --> 01:33:41.752
<i>I spent my life as a scientist. trying
to create a world without weakness. without outcasts.</i>

803
01:33:41.919 --> 01:33:46.210
<i>I sought to create a stronger human
being. but there's no such thing.</i>

804
01:33:46.293 --> 01:33:51.471
<i>Human beings are weak. pathetic.
feeble minded creatures.</i>

805
01:33:51.971 --> 01:33:56.239
<i>Why be human at all. when
we can be so much more?</i>

806
01:33:56.323 --> 01:33:59.956
<i>Faster. stronger. smarter.</i>

807
01:34:00.078 --> 01:34:03.372
<i>This is my gift to you.</i>

808
01:34:11.948 --> 01:34:13.651
OsCorp!

809
