820
01:36:29.010 --> 01:36:32.880
<i>No. no. no. Connors is on the way.</i>

821
01:36:32.987 --> 01:36:34.141
<i>He's coming to you right now.</i>
he needs the disbursement device.

822
01:36:34.250 --> 01:36:35.717
He's gonna infect the whole city...

823
01:36:35.798 --> 01:36:36.748
- There's 8 minutes left.

824
01:36:36.863 --> 01:36:38.728
