what I just told you?</i>

825
01:36:38.846 --> 01:36:42.689
<i> People are gonna die!</I>
You leave right now!
<i>Listen. that is an order. OK?!</i>

826
01:36:42.805 --> 01:36:44.083
I'm gonna get everybody out.

827
01:36:45.337 --> 01:36:49.008
Gwen! You mother
hover. are you serious?!

828
01:37:05.352 --> 01:37:06.569
He's heading south!

829
