Stand down now or we will open fire!

830
01:37:19.630 --> 01:37:22.578
<i>You are surrounded.
there is no escape!</i>

831
01:38:58.925 --> 01:39:00.368
Freeze!

832
01:39:00.931 --> 01:39:02.548
Down on the ground!

833
01:39:02.631 --> 01:39:05.691
Put your hands behind your head! Now!

834
01:39:09.243 --> 01:39:10.854
Parker!

835
01:39:12.551 --> 01:39:15.968
It's headed to Oscorp. and your
daughter is there right now!

836
01:39:29.043 --> 01:39:31.038
You got to let me go.

837
