and it is very. very strong.

841
01:40:19.241 --> 01:40:22.204
<i>Time remaining: 1 minute.</i>

842
01:41:35.295 --> 01:41:37.352
<i>Antidote complete.</i>

843
01:41:50.065 --> 01:41:51.254
Oh man...

844
