853
01:42:31.967 --> 01:42:33.805
- Yeah.
- Get him on the phone for me.

854
01:42:33.913 --> 01:42:35.989
The cops are evacuating
everybody. who the hell cares?

855
01:42:36.102 --> 01:42:37.675
Get him on the phone for me!

856
01:42:56.495 --> 01:42:59.380
Hey Charlie. get me
Enriquez from 54th street!

857
01:42:59.481 --> 01:43:01.116
Angelo get your mug over here.

858
01:43:01.221 --> 01:43:03.658
Walsky. you're getting some overtime!

859
01:43:04.890 --> 01:43:06.607
<i>All tower cranes on 6th. swing
your jib arms over the avenue.</i>

860
01:43:06.727 --> 01:43:10.165
<i>Boom angles at 90 degrees.</i>

861
01:43:10.334 --> 01:43:13.409
<i>  Spiderman needs those big boys high and lined up.</ i>

862
01:43:13.513 --> 01:43:15.734
<i>Let's give him a
clear approach. over.</i>

863
01:45:47.414 --> 01:45:49.274
Dad. 

