- No. we can stop the lizard.

866
01:45:53.375 --> 01:45:56.013
- You don't understand!
- I do.

867
01:45:56.702 --> 01:46:00.142
Your boyfriend is a man
of many masks. I get it.

868
01:46:00.547 --> 01:46:03.156
Give me this. get in the car.

869
01:46:07.428 --> 01:46:09.550
Please make sure he's OK.

870
01:46:22.236 --> 01:46:24.853
<i>Initializing GANALI device.</i>

871
01:46:24.916 --> 01:46:28.929
<i>Detonation in T minus 2 minutes.</i>

873
01:47:50.751 --> 01:47:53.680
Poor Peter Parker.

874
01:47:54.569 --> 01:47:58.349
No mother. no father.

875
01:47:59.422 --> 01:48:01.261
No uncle.

876
01:48:02.374 --> 01:48:04.835
All alone.

877
01:48:05.085 --> 01:48:07.429
He's not alone!

878
01:48:25.962 --> 01:48:29.421
<i>Detonation in T minus 45 seconds.</i>

879
01:48:37.999 --> 01:48:39.592
Hey. gift from Gwen!

880
01:48:41.370 --> 01:48:43.667
I got this Peter. go!

881
01:48:48.951 --> 01:48:51.887
<i>T minus 30 seconds.</i>

882
01:49:08.924 --> 01:49:12.678
<i>Detonation in T minus 10 seconds.</i>

883
01:49:13.599 --> 01:49:18.253
<i>9. 8. 7...</i>

884
01:49:18.908 --> 01:49:23.945
<i>6. 5. 4...</i>

885
01:49:25.103 --> 01:49:28.669
<i>3. 2. 1</i>

889
01:51:13.618 --> 01:51:15.320
The captain.

890
01:51:15.715 --> 01:51:17.377
Captain!

891
01:51:20.060 --> 01:51:23.804
- The lizard...
- It's alright. we stopped him.

892
01:51:24.660 --> 01:51:26.395
Let's get you out of here.

893
01:51:27.204 --> 01:51:28.643
Come on!

894
01:51:29.180 --> 01:51:32.000
Look at me. stay with me.

895
01:51:32.035 --> 01:51:33.211
Help is on the way. OK?

896
01:51:33.246 --> 01:51:37.820
You need to be gone.
when they get here. OK?

897
01:51:39.396 --> 01:51:43.655
- I'm not going anywhere.
- I was wrong about you Peter.

898
01:51:44.439 --> 01:51:46.633
This city needs you.

899
01:51:48.243 --> 01:51:51.925
Here. you're gonna need this.

900
01:51:55.047 --> 01:51:57.039
You're gonna make enemies.

901
01:51:59.398 --> 01:52:05.130
People will get hurt.
Sometimes people closest to you.

902
01:52:08.717 --> 01:52:11.662
So I want you to
promise me something. OK?

903
01:52:12.667 --> 01:52:16.784
Leave Gwen out of it.

904
01:52:19.122 --> 01:52:21.493
Promise me that.

905
01:52:26.287 --> 01:52:28.075
You promise me.

906
01:53:42.189 --> 01:53:45.279
<i>An eerie calm has set
in over New York city.</i>

907
01:53:45.357 --> 01:53:48.918
<i>Apparently some sort of aerosolized
antidote </i>

908
01:53:49.005 --> 01:53:54.017
<i> was launched from Oscorp Tower.
which seems to have counter acted the bio toxins.</ i>

909
01:53:54.106 --> 01:53:56.633
<i>Residents of lower Manhattan can rest peacefully.</i>

910
01:53:56.711 --> 01:53:59.729
<i>knowing that the alleged mastermind of this terror plot.</i>

911
01:53:59.822 --> 01:54:03.398
<i>Dr. Curtis Connors is behind bars.</i>

915
01:54:40.839 --> 01:54:44.086
Sweetheart. it's OK.

916
01:54:45.964 --> 01:54:50.160
It's alright.

917
01:54:50.878 --> 01:54:55.882
- Rough night.
- It's gonna be alright.

918
01:55:48.892 --> 01:55:50.685
Where have you been?

919
01:55:59.987 --> 01:56:02.012
My father died.

920
01:56:05.789 --> 01:56:07.644
There was a funeral.

921
01:56:08.909 --> 01:56:10.749
They shot 

922
