They shot rifles and made speeches.

923
01:56:18.491 --> 01:56:24.276
Two of my teachers showed up.
Flash showed up.

924
01:56:28.173 --> 01:56:30.765
Everyone was there but you.

925
01:56:45.324 --> 01:56:47.683
I can't do it.

926
01:56:49.786 --> 01:56:52.187
I'm sorry. I can't...

927
01:56:52.282 --> 01:56:55.406
- What are you saying?
